Class KerberosIdentityDataFileReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.serveraction.kerberos.AbstractKerberosDataFileReader
      • org.apache.ambari.server.serveraction.kerberos.KerberosIdentityDataFileReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Map<String,String>>, KerberosDataFile, KerberosIdentityDataFile

    public class KerberosIdentityDataFileReader
extends AbstractKerberosDataFileReader
implements KerberosIdentityDataFile
    KerberosIdentityDataFileReader is an implementation of an AbstractKerberosDataFileReader that is used to read existing Kerberos identity data files.

    This class encapsulates a CSVParser to read a CSV-formatted file.
